Cell.Text: <<Shared>> Looking to prove yourself? I may have something that needs attending to.

Node.Caption: Favor058QuestGiveTopic: Is there anything I can do for ?

Cell.Text: [S] We caught a spy, recently. He's sitting in the jail right now, waiting to be interrogated. You squeeze some words out of him, and I'll be impressed.
What do you want? You Imperials aren't getting anything out of me.
G|I'll talk. Just leave me alone.
Yeah, right. He'll let me go straight up to the executioner's block. No thanks. | You'll see. When my comrades come for me, it'll be you that's in this cell.

Node.Caption: Favor058SpyTopicNICE01: Just agree to talk, and I'm sure the Jarl will let you go.

Cell.Text: [S] G|I'll never talk, you Imperial dog.

Node.Caption: Favor058SpyTopicBRAWL01: You want to do this the hard way, huh? (Brawl)

Cell.Text: They... they wouldn't forget about me. They'll come. You'll see.

Node.Caption: Favor058SpyTopicNICE02: You hear any rescue coming? The only way you're getting out is if you talk.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Maybe you're right. Maybe it's too much to hope they'd just show up out of nowhere. | All right, tell the Jarl I'll talk.

Node.Caption: Favor058SpyTopicNICE03: Think about it. You're only one spy. They probably think you're dead already.

Cell.Text: <<Shared>> You've done a fine thing for the Hold.
<<Shared>> Shor's Crown, I wish I had more people like you in my court.
<<Shared>> Now that's what I like to hear. Keep up the good work.
<<Shared>> Now that's the kind of news this Hold needs. Good work.
<<Shared>> That's how it's done. We could use more of that kind of news around here.
<<Shared>> Now why are people like you so hard to find? You have my personal thanks.
<<Shared>> By Ysmir, if only everyone in this Hold were like you. Good job.
<<Shared>> That's what I want to hear.
<<Shared>> The Hold could use more people like you.

Node.Caption: Favor058QuestReturnTopic: The spy has agreed to talk.

Cell.Text: [S] <<Shared>> Here's a reward for your efforts.
